org.propelgraph

Interface LocatableGraph

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Graph

    public interface LocatableGraph
extends Graph
    This interface is used by Graph classes that support a LocatableGraphFactory. Of note, this interface need not be supported by a Graph class to be supported by a LocatableGraphFactory class. As part of the propelgraph-neo4j subproject we provide an example of one can work around the lack of LocatableGraph awareness in a Graph implemenation. This is done with cooperation of the LocatableGraphFactoryFactoryImpl class.
    Author:
    drewvale
